{"tid":1999122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港冇反紅媒遊行","createTime":"2020-05-03T03:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T03:12:20.000Z","uid":37554,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"98d915f0826b54413e83fe56b93bdd8367252752","tid":1999122,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T03:06:14.000Z","msg":"「拒絕紅色媒體、守護臺灣民主」遊行是指在2019年6月23日，於中華民國臺北市凱達格蘭大道舉行的大型集會遊行又稱623凱道集結。這次活動由成吉思汗健身俱樂部「館長」陳之漢、及時代力量立法委員黃國昌號召，並有數萬名民眾參與示威遊行。是反紅媒運動之一。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s.rfi.fr/media/display/e168621a-10c4-11ea-816c-005056a99247/w:980/p:16x9/64997132_615373985638949_2338879008596295680_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.rfi.fr%2Fmedia%2Fdisplay%2Fe168621a-10c4-11ea-816c-005056a99247%2Fw%3A980%2Fp%3A16x9%2F64997132_615373985638949_2338879008596295680_o.jpg&h=471ac62a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.limedia.tw/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0241-1-1068x712.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.limedia.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2FIMG_0241-1-1068x712.jpg&h=25974c02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/twapple/640pix/20190624/_Other/LA01aa001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2Ftwapple%2F640pix%2F20190624%2F_Other%2FLA01aa001.jpg&h=95ae16a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/twapple/640pix/20190624/LA02/LA02_001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2Ftwapple%2F640pix%2F20190624%2FLA02%2FLA02_001.jpg&h=0341e601&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a369df72f28c36c36e333377d6448a0fae9226da","tid":1999122,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T03:12:20.000Z","msg":"擺買或選擇性消費等如破壞自由經濟，好暴力"}]}